WEBVTT

00:00:01.345 --> 00:00:02.571
SIX O'CLOCK.

00:00:05.192 --> 00:00:07.261
TAPE SEVEN, MR BIRMAN.

00:00:07.487 --> 00:00:11.936
host ongeheybt tsu fartseyln FROM di A.K. in Lublin.

00:00:11.115 --> 00:00:14.450
yo, zey hobn zey hobn bash- gevolt ibernemen di makht.

00:00:14.811 --> 00:00:17.927
un tsum sof iz zey nisht gerotn,

00:00:18.135 --> 00:00:23.346
un zey hobn oyf- gevolt zukhn yidn tsu sh- zey hobn nor geshosn.

00:00:23.346 --> 00:00:25.861
zey hobn ayngehaltn tseger, banen,

00:00:25.861 --> 00:00:29.367
zey hobn aropgenumen yidn, arayn in vald, zey hobn geshosn, in mitn veg.

00:00:29.526 --> 00:00:35.527
un azoy az in yedern gegnt vu s'gegangen banen zenen zey geven, vayl a ban geyt adurkh nokh velder, nokh ruzhne gegnter.

00:00:35.635 --> 00:00:38.694
hot men ayngehaltn in mitn veg di ban un zey hobn aropgenumen

00:00:38.694 --> 00:00:44.910
yidn un arayn in vald arayn, geshosn. zenen geven zeyer a sakh yidn zenen gefaln nokhn bafrayen oykhet.

00:00:45.422 --> 00:00:48.566
zey vayter di dos militer, dos yidishe mit di

00:00:48.566 --> 00:00:51.528
mit di gever, zey zenen farblibn in dem

00:00:51.528 --> 00:00:56.067
Bakhst undz tsu bahitn. shtel dikh for az s'geven az s'gekumen a yontev,

00:00:56.067 --> 00:01:00.927
gedenk ikh zayendik in Lublin zenen zey geven bay di shul, front mit di mashin-gever,

00:01:00.927 --> 00:01:04.603
vayl zey hobn ongemakht khurves di A.K., zenen arayn in ale shtubn arayn.

00:01:04.845 --> 00:01:06.813
azoy az m'hot moyre gehat far zey.

00:01:07.663 --> 00:01:11.504
un ikh bin in dem bl- in Lublin geven a lengere tsayt.

00:01:11.511 --> 00:01:14.222
azoy az dort in Lublin hob ikh

00:01:14.430 --> 00:01:17.158
ongehoybn tsu zukhn a basheftikung.

00:01:18.632 --> 00:01:22.136
un ikh bin a KNIT oyfn fakh, ikh ken der KNITTING.

00:01:22.260 --> 00:01:26.743
un ikh bin gevoyer gevorn fun aza fabrik, fun aza varshtat, a groyse varshtat,

00:01:27.103 --> 00:01:32.379
un ikh bin arayn in dem varshtat arayn, geb ikh kuk, s'zitsn, der bal- ikh gey tsum balbos, ikh veys dokh ver s'der,

00:01:32.622 --> 00:01:34.489
veys ikh, direktor oder ver,

00:01:34.714 --> 00:01:38.319
zogt mir un vayzt mir der, ikh gey tsu, zey zenen tsvey yidn.

00:01:38.629 --> 00:01:41.503
zey hobn far der krig gehat di FACTORY,

00:01:41.503 --> 00:01:46.709
un zenen avek keyn Rusland un zenen tsurikgekumen un zey gobn o- ibergenumen tsurik di FACTORY.

00:01:46.709 --> 00:01:51.518
un ikh hob zey gezogt az ikh vil fardinen a por z- dos in poylish, zlotes.

00:01:51.518 --> 00:01:55.447
ikh vil fardinen epes tsu ikh zol kenen lebn, az ikh bin ersht fun di lagern gekumen.

00:01:55.605 --> 00:01:59.649
un er hot mikh tsugeshtelt tsu a mashin, iz geven bloyz kristn, shkotsim dortn,

00:01:59.824 --> 00:02:03.311
un zey hobn ale gearbet, un ikh bin geshtanen bay mayn mashin, ikh hob mir oykhet gearbet.

00:02:03.925 --> 00:02:09.487
dernokhn, azoy gey ikh a mol tsum balbos nokh a geviser tsayt onarbetn dort, er hot mir batsolt,

00:02:09.830 --> 00:02:13.363
un ikh hob shoyn gekent aynkoyfn zikh, s'geven a mark fun kol-tuv.

00:02:13.363 --> 00:02:18.954
iz geven a guter eyn ort fun Lublin iz gornisht tsehakt gevorn, zenen arayn, hot zikh untergegebn di shtot,

00:02:19.028 --> 00:02:21.809
un dortn arum un arum iz do zeyer a sakh derfer,

00:02:21.809 --> 00:02:24.897
un poyern m'hot arayngebrengt hiner un gendz un

00:02:24.897 --> 00:02:26.972
un antfl- ruzhne erley kezn,

00:02:26.972 --> 00:02:30.935
azoy az der mark iz geven ful mit esnvarg az hob ikh shoyn nisht gezen azoy fil yorn.

00:02:31.127 --> 00:02:34.229
farshteyst, bin ikh mikh bay dem tsugegangen tsu dem

00:02:34.229 --> 00:02:37.247
tsu dem eygntimer, un ikh hob im gezogt, efsher kenstu

00:02:37.303 --> 00:02:43.096
epes ikh zol nisht darfn shteyn bay di m- neyn, farkert, er iz tsugekumen tsu mir, zogt er, a yid,

00:02:43.096 --> 00:02:49.458
nokh azelkhe lagern, darfstu shteyn bay a mashin arbetn punkt azoy vi di poyern, ot er azoy gerufene.

00:02:49.458 --> 00:02:51.422
vayl er iz dokh oykhet geven oyfgekokht

00:02:51.529 --> 00:02:56.147
beyz oyf di khevre. er hot zey gehaltn vayl er hot zey badorfn hobn, s'nisht geven keyn yidn nokh dem.

00:02:56.693 --> 00:02:58.830
du vest shteyn bay a mashin arbetn? neyn!

00:02:59.089 --> 00:03:01.077
arayngerufn nokhn magazin arayn,

00:03:01.077 --> 00:03:04.584
un er hot mir aroysgegebn fertike zakhn az ikh zol geyn oyfn MARKET

00:03:04.742 --> 00:03:07.599
un farkoyfn, un handlen, onheybn handlen.

00:03:07.599 --> 00:03:11.058
un azoy iz geven, er hot mir aroysgegebn damen-zokn un ruzhne erley

00:03:11.058 --> 00:03:14.895
andere mayses, sveters, un ikh hob farkoyft un ikh hob mir gants sheyn fardint.

00:03:14.985 --> 00:03:18.407
un ikh hob im gedankt un azoy opgezisn in Lublin,

00:03:18.407 --> 00:03:20.272
a lengere tsayt. nokh dem

00:03:20.272 --> 00:03:23.453
iz shoyn ongekumen shtitse fun Hilfs Fond, fun

00:03:23.453 --> 00:03:29.647
fun oysland, veys ikh, fun Unra, m'hot shoyn fun di magazinen aroysnemen andere ontuekhtser.

00:03:29.647 --> 00:03:33.609
azoy s'gegangen op a lebn. in tsvishn tsayt, zayendik in Lublin,

00:03:34.645 --> 00:03:36.461
mayn froy, yetstike,

00:03:36.518 --> 00:03:39.600
iz geven fun Rusland tsurikgekumen,

00:03:39.977 --> 00:03:43.379
mit der mame, un mit nokh tsvey shvestern,

00:03:43.723 --> 00:03:45.387
hobn gevoynt in dem

00:03:45.428 --> 00:03:48.324
in in dem hoyz, in Perets hoyz, m'geyt zikh azoy.

00:03:48.347 --> 00:03:52.391
hot zikh di mame, zi iz a feike froy geven, zi lebt shoyn haynt nisht,

00:03:53.292 --> 00:03:55.075
hot zikh gemakht a kokh.

00:03:55.873 --> 00:04:00.339
mentshn fardinen shoyn a bisl in gas, m'loyft shoyn arop, m'fardint, s'do gelt, m'ken fardinen.

00:04:00.632 --> 00:04:04.355
a gute kukhn iz zi, zi hot gekent gut sheyn kokhn, yidishe maykholim,

00:04:04.598 --> 00:04:10.397
hot zi ongehoybn tsu kokhn un gebn mitog dortn, mentshn zenen gekumen esn mitog. un tsvishn andere bin ikh oykhet arayn esn mitog.

00:04:11.027 --> 00:04:13.133
eyn mol, tsvey mol, dray mol.

00:04:13.133 --> 00:04:17.723
nokh dem hot zikh dort iz dort geven a zal vu m'hot zikh tsunoyfgenumen nokh a geviser tsayt,

00:04:17.723 --> 00:04:19.948
gemakht zikh a tants-ovnt,

00:04:20.427 --> 00:04:23.323
un s'geven a kleyner vos hot tsugeshpilt,

00:04:23.329 --> 00:04:28.419
un un m'hot getantst shoyn un tsvishn andere iz geven m- mayn ershtike froy,

00:04:28.847 --> 00:04:30.978
i- ikh hob ir farbetn tsum tantsn.

00:04:30.978 --> 00:04:34.528
hob ikh mit ir getantst eyn mol, tsvey mol, ikh bin gut in tantsn.

00:04:34.770 --> 00:04:36.941
ikh hob a mol gelernt tantsn far der krig.

00:04:37.015 --> 00:04:38.561
un ir hot es gefoln.

00:04:39.208 --> 00:04:44.310
shoyn, azoy iz mir opgegangen a tsayt, m'hot zikh farvaylt tsuzamen, m'hot gegesn, m'iz aroysgegangen a mol,

00:04:44.310 --> 00:04:46.138
azoy hot men zikh bakent.

00:04:46.431 --> 00:04:49.192
in tsvishn tsayt bin ikh nokh avek

00:04:49.468 --> 00:04:52.111
ikh bin avek, nokh zi iz nokh nisht geven farheyrat,

00:04:52.489 --> 00:04:55.776
ikh hob oyf a ku- ikh hob gezogt ikh gey forn avek oyf a kurtser tsayt.

00:04:55.776 --> 00:04:58.459
dort hot men nokh gekent fardinen meyn a por,

00:04:58.459 --> 00:05:02.506
vayl ikh bin arayn in doytshishn gegnt arayn. vos heyst in doytshishn? di Poyln,

00:05:02.783 --> 00:05:06.776
di doytshn zenen dertlofn fun dem gegnt, di polyakn hobn dos ibergenumen.

00:05:06.917 --> 00:05:09.960
bin ikh arayn in di gevezene gegnter fun di doytshn,

00:05:09.960 --> 00:05:14.099
bin ikh arayn, dos iz geven Nidershlezye, heyst es oyf doytshish.

00:05:14.325 --> 00:05:18.675
arayn in a shtot arayn, a groyse shtot, di shtot vu ikh bin adurkhgegangen in di lagern,

00:05:18.675 --> 00:05:20.630
Bro- Breslau, UNK.

00:05:20.873 --> 00:05:25.440
un dortn iz geven a groyse shtot, iz geven a zeyer polyakn, gesheftn, s'geven a a handl.

00:05:25.868 --> 00:05:29.459
un dort bin ikh arayn un dort hob ikh getrofn oykhet a yid vos hot gehat

00:05:29.459 --> 00:05:34.671
a zeyfn-geve- a zeyfn-fabrik vos er hot gemakht zeyf. oysgearbet zeyf.

00:05:35.453 --> 00:05:37.489
fun fets, aroys gearbet zeyf.

00:05:37.579 --> 00:05:40.475
ikh bin dortn arayn, hot er mir gegebn ikh zol arumforn

00:05:40.515 --> 00:05:43.226
mitn tram, tsi in gevelber arayn farkoyfn.

00:05:43.266 --> 00:05:44.967
ikh hob zikh UNK tsu fardint.

00:05:44.967 --> 00:05:46.567
nokh a geviser tsayt,

00:05:46.708 --> 00:05:49.554
iz der bruder oykhet gekumen fun Rusland,

00:05:49.577 --> 00:05:51.911
iz der eyntsiker vos ikh hob gezogt er

00:05:51.911 --> 00:05:54.869
er iz geven in Rusland, der eyner vos iz geven in PALESTINE.

00:05:55.028 --> 00:05:58.363
iz eyn bruder, er iz yinger fun mir a sakh,

00:05:58.842 --> 00:06:02.711
hot iz er gegangen arum in di in di in di in di

00:06:02.711 --> 00:06:05.602
in di shtetlekh arayn, in di shtet arayn,

00:06:05.608 --> 00:06:09.095
un zukhn adresn, zukhn a Birman, zukhn efsher ver iz geblibn.

00:06:09.355 --> 00:06:11.661
akht brider zol men nisht kenen trefn vemen?

00:06:12.173 --> 00:06:17.080
un er hot gezukht un gezokht un arayn dort in dem Varshe in dem Prage, er iz arayn.

00:06:17.080 --> 00:06:18.647
neyn, zi hot im gezogt,

00:06:18.653 --> 00:06:20.894
d- di mayn ershtike froy,

00:06:20.894 --> 00:06:23.863
hot gezogt a Birman iz, er iz gekumen keyn Lublin oykhet,

00:06:23.863 --> 00:06:26.960
az do a Birman, iz er avek nokh Nidershlezye,

00:06:26.960 --> 00:06:30.122
un er iz nishto do, hot gezogt er vet kumen in a kurtser tsayt.

00:06:30.128 --> 00:06:36.225
er hot gehert Nidershlezye, er hot oykhet gevoynt in Nidershlezye, nisht vayt fun Brodslav, in a kleyn shtetl, oykhet gevoynt.

00:06:36.225 --> 00:06:41.563
un er iz geven a magaziner a bisl fun di Unra zakhn, er hot aroysgeteylt mentshn zakhn,

00:06:41.569 --> 00:06:46.544
er hot shoyn gehat a shtikl pozitsyon, a po- po- po- POSITION. farshteyst?

00:06:46.544 --> 00:06:50.299
un hot er mir gezogt, veystu vos? ikh bin geven in Lublin,

00:06:50.299 --> 00:06:54.574
un un ikh hob geredt mit dayn ba- bakanter, mit di heyst zi, mit dem GIRLFRIEND,

00:06:54.580 --> 00:07:00.649
un zi zogt az zi zi hot gezogt im az ikh vel do bald kumen, un m'zet nisht un m'hert nisht, dortn bin ikh geven farnumen.

00:07:00.807 --> 00:07:04.682
un ikh hob ongehoybn shraybn ir a briv az s'vet nisht gedoyern lang, ikh vel tsurik.

00:07:04.890 --> 00:07:08.270
un zi iz geven in dem Perets hoyz, mit der mame mit di tsvey shvestern.

00:07:08.270 --> 00:07:12.545
s'nokh a mol ongekumen nokh a shvoger iz ongekumen fun Rusisher militer.

00:07:12.940 --> 00:07:18.199
yo, un nokh a kurtser tsayt hobn di mentshn, heyst za- ir muter,

00:07:18.778 --> 00:07:20.209
mit der gantser familye,

00:07:20.209 --> 00:07:23.750
zikh arayngetsoygn oykhet keyn Nidershlezye vu vu doytshn hobn gevoynt.

00:07:23.807 --> 00:07:26.399
dort hot men gekent krign a dire umzist.

00:07:26.423 --> 00:07:28.073
groyse sh- tsimern,

00:07:28.073 --> 00:07:30.883
a eyne iz geven tsvey dray timsern mit a kokh,

00:07:30.883 --> 00:07:33.819
mit a ⟨lebedi⟩, veyst nokh vi nokh a doytsher hot lib gehat tsu lebn.

00:07:33.819 --> 00:07:36.544
un di doytshn zenen dertlofn, hobn mir zey aroysgeyogt,

00:07:36.544 --> 00:07:41.587
nor s'geven a sakh derfer vos s'geven doytshn, zey hobn nokh geven, m'hot zey nokh nisht getshepet.

00:07:41.695 --> 00:07:43.579
in di derfer arayn,

00:07:43.703 --> 00:07:49.893
ven ikh bin arayn shoyn keyn ⟨Doln un Shlosn⟩, der bruder iz tsurikgekumen keyn Nidershlezye mikh zukhn,

00:07:49.893 --> 00:07:54.851
un er hot shoyn gevust vu ven vos, vayl zi hot oyfgegebn vu di vu di voynung,

00:07:54.992 --> 00:07:56.482
un er hot mikh getrofn.

00:07:56.482 --> 00:07:58.243
voser a min, ir veyst vifl yorn!

00:07:58.283 --> 00:08:01.992
di gantse milkhome, un er iz geven in poylishn militer frierte.

00:08:01.992 --> 00:08:03.912
azoy m'hot zikh shoyn lang nisht gezen.

00:08:04.341 --> 00:08:08.126
un yo, iz hobn zey zikh, di familye,

00:08:08.126 --> 00:08:12.834
zikh getoysht un s'do geven shver zey tsu tsu lebn.

00:08:12.834 --> 00:08:17.227
fun dem zitsn in kokh in kokhn a bisl mitog ken men nisht eybik zitsn.

00:08:17.250 --> 00:08:25.107
un hobn gezogt m'vet adurkhforn keyn keyn Nidershlezye dort. dort vet men gefinen a dire, m'vet hobn biz dos, zenen dokh gelign oyf nares, oyf militer nares.

00:08:25.333 --> 00:08:27.135
un zenen dortn ahingekumen,

00:08:27.135 --> 00:08:33.303
un zenen geven in Dzhirzhoyni oyf a shtot, oykhet geven a gevezene doytshishe shtot, hot gehert tsu Poyln.

00:08:33.303 --> 00:08:35.115
un zey hobn zikh dort bazetst,

00:08:35.155 --> 00:08:38.895
zi hot ongehoybn, zi hot a zi hot a bisl, zi hot EDUCATION.

00:08:39.255 --> 00:08:44.244
UNK zi di HIGH SCHOOL hot zi gekrogn UNK, zi hot shoyn bald gehaltn bay UNIVERSITY.

00:08:44.757 --> 00:08:49.374
zi iz alt geven zibetsn yor ven di krig hot oysge⟨UNK⟩ in akhtstn yor, azoy az zi hot shoyn geendikt

00:08:49.701 --> 00:08:54.167
di andere halb, nokh nisht di andere alb hot zi shoyn gehaltn bay endikn, un di krig hot oysgebrokhn.

00:08:54.375 --> 00:08:57.507
un zi iz dortn arayn in an OFFICE arayn arbetn,

00:08:57.987 --> 00:09:02.334
in an O- a fabrik vos hot oysgearbet radyo radyo aparatn.

00:09:02.695 --> 00:09:05.695
un zi iz dortn geven in der OFFICE,

00:09:05.695 --> 00:09:09.441
un der shvoger vos er iz gekumen fun Rusland, ir's a shvester's a man,

00:09:09.441 --> 00:09:12.707
iz oykhet dortn gevorn a shtikl makher vayl er iz geven vayter a

00:09:12.707 --> 00:09:17.083
hot shtudirt als advokat, als SOLICITOR, oykhet a inteligenter khevre.

00:09:17.173 --> 00:09:21.571
azoy zey hobn gezukht arayn mentshn vos m'ken onfirn mit a fabrik.

00:09:21.645 --> 00:09:25.633
un er iz geven a bukhhalter oykhet, er hot gekent haltn di bikher,

00:09:25.633 --> 00:09:28.541
azoy er hot dortn gearbet, zi hot gearbet in der OFFICE,

00:09:28.615 --> 00:09:31.781
un shoyn. nokh a geviser tsayt bin ikh ahingekumen dortn,

00:09:31.855 --> 00:09:34.498
un m'hot bashlosn khasene tsu hobn.

00:09:35.010 --> 00:09:38.357
un m'hot dortn in dem Dolner Shlos, Nidershlezye

00:09:38.357 --> 00:09:42.615
dortn khasene un gedenk ikh shoyn bay shvoger in shtub, bay im in shtub,

00:09:43.313 --> 00:09:45.857
hot men gemakht geven a groyse shtub, er hot farbetn ale

00:09:45.857 --> 00:09:48.318
fun zayn OFFICE un di froy,

00:09:48.477 --> 00:09:53.449
un dos iz geven dos iz geven m'hot zikh khasene gehat.

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:54.951
gedenkst di date?

00:09:55.092 --> 00:09:56.368
di date? yo.

00:09:57.015 --> 00:09:58.663
in nayn un fertsikstn.

00:09:59.766 --> 00:10:02.915
nayn un fertsikstn, in fuftsikstn iz er geboyrn gevorn.

00:10:03.124 --> 00:10:08.315
in nayn un fertsikstn yor hot men khasene gehat, nokh dem nokh dem tsum yor iz geboyrn gevorn

00:10:08.878 --> 00:10:14.964
Myetek, MAX, un in fir yor arum iz geboyrn gevorn di tokhter.

00:10:15.915 --> 00:10:18.575
azoy az di tsvey kinder hob ikh gehat,

00:10:18.767 --> 00:10:23.772
un dort hot men shoyn gehat bakvemt, m'hot shoyn gevoynt bakvemt, un,

00:10:22.446 --> 00:10:28.447
vi hot geheysn di sh- di di shtot, di di ertl?

00:10:26.260 --> 00:10:27.874
di shtot iz geven,

00:10:27.947 --> 00:10:30.239
neyn, undz zenen mir, ikh bin arayn keyn

00:10:30.239 --> 00:10:32.430
keyn Dzhirzhonye vu m'hot khasene gehat.

00:10:32.588 --> 00:10:34.725
vu zey, di gantse familye, hot gevoynt.

00:10:34.984 --> 00:10:36.463
bin ikh dortn geven.

00:10:36.621 --> 00:10:38.353
nokh dem bin ikh arayn,

00:10:39.068 --> 00:10:42.018
ikh far dem, eyder ikh hob nokh khasene gehat, bin ikh geven

00:10:42.018 --> 00:10:47.009
in a shtot vos s'hot geheysn Vrodslov, heyst es Valbzhikh.

00:10:47.286 --> 00:10:51.906
Valbzhikh un zey dortn oykhet geven, dortn hob ikh vayter getrofn a kuzin.

00:10:51.906 --> 00:10:55.804
takesh dem Binyamin vos ikh hob dir gezogt, dem Hershl's zun,

00:10:55.804 --> 00:10:59.643
hob ikh getrofn, er hot gearbet in di kompanye, nor er hot nisht gearbet unter der erd,

00:10:59.643 --> 00:11:02.352
nor oykhet in an OFFICE, iz dort hot er gehat a bisl nere,

00:11:02.352 --> 00:11:05.300
azoy er iz dort geven. azoy dort hob ikh im getrofn, ikh hob dortn

00:11:05.352 --> 00:11:06.682
a bisl, dernokh hobn mir,

00:11:06.682 --> 00:11:10.592
bin ikh avek keyn Dzhirzhonye, ikh hob mikh getrofn mit ir vu zey zenen ongekumen,

00:11:10.658 --> 00:11:12.879
un azoy iz azoy iz geven.

00:11:13.020 --> 00:11:15.815
azoy hot men tsuzamen gelebt, ongehoybn tsu lebn,

00:11:15.973 --> 00:11:17.924
un s'geboyrn kinder,

00:11:18.437 --> 00:11:20.878
un vi lang hostu gevoynt in Poyln?

00:11:20.800 --> 00:11:24.810
in Poyln hob ikh gevoynt bizn in zekhtsikster yor, in

00:11:25.204 --> 00:11:27.645
in letstn khoydesh in zekhtsikstn yor bi-

00:11:27.887 --> 00:11:29.647
bin ikh aroys, heyst es

00:11:29.647 --> 00:11:33.804
farn farn vi nokh heyst es, der letster khoydesh, der

00:11:33.405 --> 00:11:34.698
detsember.

00:11:34.249 --> 00:11:36.887
detsember. ikh farges di dates.

00:11:36.887 --> 00:11:39.013
un in detsember,

00:11:39.013 --> 00:11:44.430
mir zenen do ongekumen keyn keyn m- Australye,

00:11:44.430 --> 00:11:48.486
iz shoyn geven iz geven punkt in nay yor.

00:11:48.610 --> 00:11:51.591
azoy far nay yor, iz nokh geven CHRISTMAS TIME.

00:11:51.883 --> 00:11:55.404
azoy az m'iz ongekumen in di tsayt do aher.

00:11:56.288 --> 00:12:00.028
un s'nokh dortn do a sakh zakhn vos ikh badorf UNK, ober s'makht nisht oys.

00:12:00.304 --> 00:12:02.002
m'ken nisht tsu fil tsien.

00:12:01.705 --> 00:12:04.596
far vos, far vos hostu,

00:12:02.177 --> 00:12:03.926
iz iz in,

00:12:05.215 --> 00:12:06.407
UNK.

00:12:05.316 --> 00:12:07.571
gevolt kumen tsu AUSTRALIA?

00:12:07.543 --> 00:12:10.358
a yo, tsu Australye hob ikh gevolt kumen

00:12:10.358 --> 00:12:13.241
azoy zey, di familye iz kurts

00:12:13.551 --> 00:12:15.755
kurts zayendik in Poyln,

00:12:15.762 --> 00:12:18.962
hobn zey gevolt, s'demolts geven a groyse emigratsye keyn

00:12:19.221 --> 00:12:21.003
keyn demolts keyn Yizrael.

00:12:21.837 --> 00:12:25.526
un di familye hot zikh nokh a gevise tsayt zikh ibergetrogn keyn Yizrael.

00:12:26.089 --> 00:12:29.492
di mame ire, mit di shvestern, mit der shvoger, mit di gantse khevre.

00:12:30.122 --> 00:12:32.279
un ikh bin farblibn in Poyln,

00:12:32.279 --> 00:12:34.469
ikh bin arayn keyn Lodzh,

00:12:34.948 --> 00:12:38.857
un dortn hob ikh ge- ongehoybn tsu arbetn bay ye- bay a tsveytn.

00:12:38.880 --> 00:12:42.856
oykhet di sandaln vi ikh hob a mol gemakht bay zikh far der krig,

00:12:42.964 --> 00:12:47.126
hobn zikh yidishe mentshn oyfgeefnt zikh azelkhe varshtatlekh, kleyntshike,

00:12:47.284 --> 00:12:49.668
un ikh bin arum un ikh bin geven a mashiner.

00:12:49.668 --> 00:12:51.463
ikh hob nor gekent arumneyen.

00:12:51.722 --> 00:12:53.842
un zey hobn nisht gehat keyn zanem.

00:12:53.882 --> 00:12:56.317
keyn za fakhman. s'geven zeyer shver tsu krign

00:12:56.317 --> 00:12:58.857
a mentsh zol kenen arumdreyen a sandal,

00:12:58.857 --> 00:13:00.609
es zol arayn di shtekh

00:13:00.666 --> 00:13:03.253
zoln arayn in di z- in di zoyl arayn,

00:13:03.253 --> 00:13:06.358
az s'zol zey nisht oystretn. farshteyst, s'geven zeyer shver.

00:13:06.358 --> 00:13:08.557
un ikh bin geven in dem kvalifitsirt.

00:13:08.682 --> 00:13:12.804
hobn mikh di di kleyne varshtatn ongehoybn mikh tsu shlepn, eyner do, eyner dortn,

00:13:12.804 --> 00:13:16.981
umetum, bay nakht hot men mikh fun bet aroysgenumen, iz geven zeyer shver

00:13:16.981 --> 00:13:21.115
vayter mittsuarbetn nokh aza krig vayter in di varshtat. zey hobn mikh nisht opgelozt.

00:13:21.115 --> 00:13:26.102
zey hobn badorfn dos hobn, azoy az s'geven

00:13:26.102 --> 00:13:28.892
UNK. un nokh a geviser tsayt, zayendik in Lodzh,

00:13:29.083 --> 00:13:36.277
hob ikh di froy aropgenumen arayn keyn Lodzh, ho'mir dortn shoyn gehat a dire, vayl zey hobn nisht gevolt dortn

00:13:36.277 --> 00:13:42.881
araynlozn registrirn mentshn fun andere shtet keyn Varshe, vayl s'geven an onloyf mistam, ver veyst.

00:13:43.191 --> 00:13:45.733
un ikh hob ir aribergenumen, m'hot gevoynt tsuzamen.

00:13:45.773 --> 00:13:48.298
dem- demolts hob ikh shoyn gehat tsvey kinder.

00:13:49.401 --> 00:13:52.955
un ikh hob zikh aleyn gemakht a varshtat far zikh di zelbe zakh.

00:13:53.569 --> 00:13:57.984
ikh hob fardint bay dem arumloyfn tsvishn di dos, zey hobn mir gut batsolt, vayl zey hobn mikh badorfn.

00:13:58.024 --> 00:14:02.181
hob ikh ongeklibn a sheyn bisl gelt, ikh hob opgekoyft bay eynem a varshtat,

00:14:02.181 --> 00:14:04.026
vos er iz geforn keyn Yizrael,

00:14:04.268 --> 00:14:07.569
ikh hob es opgekoyft in bay dem varshtat hob ikh gemakht zeyer sheyn.

00:14:07.896 --> 00:14:10.303
ikh hob ongehoybn tsu handlen mit di kristn,

00:14:10.360 --> 00:14:12.902
avekgeshikt skhoyre in ruzhne shtet arayn,

00:14:12.925 --> 00:14:17.334
azoy az s'iz geven, oyb es geyt materyelns iz undz geven zeyer gut.

00:14:17.334 --> 00:14:21.221
di froy hot gehat a dinst bay zikh, a kristlekhe,

00:14:21.480 --> 00:14:24.899
un m'geforn avek oyf HOLIDAYS, zeyer oyf tsvey monatn,

00:14:25.125 --> 00:14:26.604
azoy az m'hot gehat

00:14:26.695 --> 00:14:28.885
a b- a bisl tsayt hot men gehat

00:14:28.885 --> 00:14:31.177
zeyer gut. no- nokh dem hot zikh gemakht

00:14:31.470 --> 00:14:33.913
di antisemitn, di antisemitishe

00:14:33.913 --> 00:14:39.311
iz geven zeyer groys. far vos? vayl demolt hot zikh getoysht, in zibn un fuftsikst- heyst es in zibn un

00:14:39.486 --> 00:14:43.968
in zibn un, yo un zibn un fuftsikstn yor,

00:14:44.008 --> 00:14:49.149
hot zikh getoysht regirung in Poyln. s'iz aropgekumen an antisemit er hot ibergenumen

00:14:49.155 --> 00:14:53.739
un er hot gevolt di yidn patern di yidn aroys fun Poyln.

00:14:53.931 --> 00:14:55.325
s'zol zayn JUDENREIN.

00:14:55.720 --> 00:14:59.986
er hot ongehoybn tsu UNK velkhe zenen gezitsn oyf groyse pozitsyes,

00:14:59.986 --> 00:15:04.826
tsvishn andere, mayn shvoger, ir shvester's man,

00:15:05.203 --> 00:15:08.800
hot men gezitsn, er iz geven a direktor in takesh in a groyser fabrik,

00:15:08.865 --> 00:15:13.950
er er hot zikh ayngeshribn in der partey, in der komunistisher partey, tsu krign a groyse pozitsye.

00:15:13.950 --> 00:15:16.048
er iz vayt geven fun komunizm,

00:15:16.138 --> 00:15:20.880
hot er ayngeshribn zikh, m'hot im gegebn aza hoykhe pozitsye. er iz geven a direktor fun a groyser fabrik.

00:15:21.353 --> 00:15:27.034
azoy vi s'ongekumen di antisemitizm, ven s'hot ibergenumen di makht, der firer hot geheysn Gormunka.

00:15:27.681 --> 00:15:31.944
un der Gormunka hot aroysgegebn azelkhe bafeln, er hot azoy gemordevet,

00:15:32.018 --> 00:15:35.820
un un s'hot zikh ongehoybn, di Endekes hobn ongehoybn oyftsuheybn dem kop,

00:15:35.820 --> 00:15:38.402
barn komunizm hot men gelozt nokh undz lebn.

00:15:38.402 --> 00:15:40.534
m'hot undz ge⟨UNK⟩, m'iz geven glaykh,

00:15:40.641 --> 00:15:43.515
m'hot gekent makhn kleyntshike fabrikelekh,

00:15:43.515 --> 00:15:48.229
private, vos m'ken nor haltn a mentsh oder tsvey, nisht keyn groyse, kleyntshike.

00:15:48.420 --> 00:15:50.096
far zikh, m'hot badorfn

00:15:50.096 --> 00:15:52.953
baleygn an ekzamen tsu kenen dem fakh arbetn.

00:15:53.331 --> 00:15:55.907
farshteyst, un dos bin ikh geven eyner fun dem.

00:15:56.200 --> 00:16:01.208
un yo, hot men m'hot gut gelebt, m'iz geforn zikh aroys.

00:16:01.208 --> 00:16:07.519
iz der shvoger, hot men genumen, m'hot aroysgevorfn, nisht aroy- geheysn im aheymgeyn,

00:16:07.519 --> 00:16:11.443
m'hot zey kimat, m'hot gezogt az m'hot zey aroysgefirt mit azelkhe vegelekh,

00:16:11.443 --> 00:16:13.637
dos iz vayzn far der velt vos far

00:16:13.637 --> 00:16:16.494
vos far a d- sort mentsh er iz, azoy vi di doytshn hobn gemakht.

00:16:16.737 --> 00:16:18.874
un aza direktor, aza kop!

00:16:19.150 --> 00:16:25.010
geven va- un dos iz geven ale fabrikn, hobn ongehoybn aroys tsuhakn. undz ze'mir oykhet gevoyer gevorn fun derfun,

00:16:25.010 --> 00:16:29.572
un zey hobn zikh ongehoybn tsu dertloyfn, veln tsu dertloyfn, lomir shoyn nisht do zitsn in dem fayer.

00:16:29.832 --> 00:16:35.937
vayl tsu mir iz arayngekumen in varshtat arayn a mol a POLICE man khapn ikh zol im gebn in der hant arayn epes gelt.

00:16:35.937 --> 00:16:38.515
ikh hob im gegebn a mol a shnepsele a bisl bronfn.

00:16:38.657 --> 00:16:40.406
zoln zikh nisht tshepen tsu mir.

00:16:40.530 --> 00:16:43.899
hobn zey ge- zogt er az hersht iz enker sof.

00:16:44.749 --> 00:16:46.464
tsu tsu mir azoy.

00:16:46.470 --> 00:16:48.753
hot er gezogt az in gas shmuest men

00:16:48.753 --> 00:16:52.795
az dos iz di yidn der sof fun di yidn, az Gormunka iz do bay der makht.

00:16:52.795 --> 00:16:55.048
oder m'vet undz aroys hakn, oder m'vet enk

00:16:55.048 --> 00:16:56.825
ikh veys ruzhne zakhn ontun aza.

00:16:57.253 --> 00:16:59.039
m'hot dos gehert, un zey hobn gehert,

00:16:59.039 --> 00:17:01.984
hot men zikh ongehoybn tsu arbetn. peser hot men aroysgegebn,

00:17:01.984 --> 00:17:04.740
vos mer kedey m'zol aroys hakn di yidn fun Poyln.

00:17:04.813 --> 00:17:08.148
un takesh, di gantse mishpokhe hot zikh arayngekhapt keyn Yisroel.

00:17:08.914 --> 00:17:10.832
ikh bin geblibn nokh in Poyln,

00:17:10.838 --> 00:17:17.109
vayl ikh hob nisht gekrign, ikh hob epes tsvey mol opgegebn un m'hot mir opgerufn. a sakh mentshn hot men opgezogt aroysforn.

00:17:17.115 --> 00:17:18.526
mir hot men opgezogt.

00:17:18.853 --> 00:17:21.002
oft hot men opgezogt di ershte mol.

00:17:21.002 --> 00:17:22.628
nokh a mol un nokh a mol.

00:17:22.785 --> 00:17:26.052
azoy zey zenen aroys epes in zibn un fuftsikstn dakht zikh mir.

00:17:26.278 --> 00:17:29.692
zey zenen aroys frierte fun undz, tsu a yor frierte, ikh gedenk nisht genoy.

00:17:29.692 --> 00:17:32.232
zey zenen aroys aroysgegangen, in Yisroel iz geven

00:17:32.232 --> 00:17:34.839
azan onloyf fun di poylishe emigratsye,

00:17:34.839 --> 00:17:37.505
az m'hot zey gegebn azelkhe erter vu tsu zayn,

00:17:37.505 --> 00:17:39.362
azelkhe blekhene hayzkes,

00:17:39.362 --> 00:17:42.388
di zun zi di zun hot gebrent in aza

00:17:42.411 --> 00:17:46.793
a dos in vi nokh heyst es, a kr- a land vos iz heys brent,

00:17:47.170 --> 00:17:52.153
un hobn undz ge- zey hobn undz geshikt a briv, zey hobn gehat undzere adres,

00:17:52.153 --> 00:17:57.637
hot men hobn zey undz ge- m'hot geshribn azoy, her oys, ikh hob mir dortn oysgearbet zikh, zayendik in Lodzh,

00:17:57.637 --> 00:18:01.338
hob ikh mir aroys gearbet fun a Bundishn mentsh, vos er iz geven in Bund,

00:18:01.378 --> 00:18:04.544
er iz geven mayn's a shokhn fun dem varshtat vu ikh hob gearbet,

00:18:05.209 --> 00:18:07.543
zo- un un in Frankraykh

00:18:07.543 --> 00:18:10.023
iz der balbos fun land iz geven a yid,

00:18:10.023 --> 00:18:11.914
a geviser Blum ver es veyst,

00:18:11.914 --> 00:18:16.678
er iz geven der der der premyer, vi der PRIME MIN- der onfirer fun land.

00:18:16.802 --> 00:18:18.689
er hot gekrign dos benkl,

00:18:18.689 --> 00:18:23.360
far der arbeter partey, er iz gekumen tsu der makht, un er iz geven in Bund, der der Blum,

00:18:23.417 --> 00:18:27.039
iz er aroyfgezetst gevorn oyfn hekhstn benkl, vayl yidn zenen feik,

00:18:27.079 --> 00:18:29.385
un m'ken zey zetsn oyf a hoykh benkl.

00:18:29.745 --> 00:18:33.446
iz der der tsulib dem vos er iz dortn gezisn, aza

00:18:33.446 --> 00:18:35.960
ts- a yidn, un oyfn hekhstn amt,

00:18:35.960 --> 00:18:39.630
hob ikh gebetn dem Bundist er zol efsher arop shraybn tsun im

00:18:39.630 --> 00:18:44.980
az ikh vil araynforn keyn Frankraykh. er hot bakant mit a groy mit tsvey kinderlekh,

00:18:44.980 --> 00:18:48.938
tsu er kenen undz oysarbetn a PERMIT arayntsuforn keyn Frankraykh.

00:18:48.938 --> 00:18:50.355
s'hot nisht lang gedoyert,

00:18:50.355 --> 00:18:56.211
ikh hob gekrign a a shte- a a langn, s'geven arayntsuforn keyn Frankraykh nor

00:18:56.211 --> 00:18:59.467
a CHWILOWY, oyf zayn oyf a yor, oyf a halb yor un arbetn,

00:18:59.467 --> 00:19:02.021
un s'geven mentshn vos hobn gekent voynen shtendik.

00:19:02.061 --> 00:19:05.490
mir hot er oysgearbet a pas shtendik tsu zayn in Frankraykh.

00:19:06.280 --> 00:19:08.487
nu un ikh hob sh- ikh hob shoyn gehat

00:19:08.487 --> 00:19:10.695
ikh hob shoyn gehat a Yisroel pas oykhet.

00:19:10.718 --> 00:19:12.737
ikh hob gehat dr- ikh hob gehat tsvey peser.

00:19:13.013 --> 00:19:17.849
zitst men un m'trakht, m'trakht vos m'tut, tsi in Frankraykh, tsi Yisroel.

00:19:18.177 --> 00:19:21.444
dervayl krigt men a briv fun Yisroel, shraybn zey azoy.

00:19:22.210 --> 00:19:24.262
zi heyst dokh Klara. Klara,

00:19:25.011 --> 00:19:30.236
zolst visn, tomer hostu an ort vu tsu forn ergets andersh oyf dervayl,

00:19:30.478 --> 00:19:33.391
vayl s'a shver lebn. tsvey kleyne kinderlekh,

00:19:33.448 --> 00:19:34.758
vest erdishet vern.

00:19:35.170 --> 00:19:37.948
di imigratsye groys, fun ale zaytn kumt men.

00:19:38.528 --> 00:19:41.407
farshteyst. hob ikh shoyn gehert azan briv,

00:19:41.717 --> 00:19:46.875
zi hot gevoynt in a kleyn shtetl, Pinsk, fun far der krig.

00:19:47.050 --> 00:19:49.164
s'hot a mol gehert nokh tsu Rusland.

00:19:49.164 --> 00:19:51.161
nakher iz es geven in poylishe hent.

00:19:51.555 --> 00:19:58.434
Pinsk, zi hot dortn shtudirt in Pinsk, der tate hot dortn shtudirt nokh ven der tsar iz geven der Rusisher tsar,

00:19:58.761 --> 00:20:01.972
azoy az der tate irer hot gehat a

00:20:01.972 --> 00:20:04.526
a CHEMIST, a a er iz geven oyfzeer.

00:20:05.072 --> 00:20:07.625
er hot geendikt a a CHEMIST iz er geven.

00:20:07.625 --> 00:20:10.381
er hot gehat a sheyn gevelb dort, zey zenen geven WELL OFF,

00:20:11.012 --> 00:20:14.257
du farshteyst, iz hot men ariber geshribn

00:20:14.257 --> 00:20:19.168
keyn in dem Pinsk shtetl arayn, az ikh zukh oys,

00:20:19.168 --> 00:20:22.720
zolstu visn, ikh heys Ayznberg, zi heyst Ayznberg fun der heym,

00:20:22.875 --> 00:20:26.649
ikh heys Ayznberg, mistam kenst ets dem tatn,

00:20:27.887 --> 00:20:30.297
vayl in aza kleyn shtetele,

00:20:30.297 --> 00:20:33.562
iz geven bakant a CHEMIST. er hot gemakht aleyn,

00:20:33.562 --> 00:20:38.718
meditsinen, ikh meyn s'nisht a mol geven amolike tsaytn azoy vi do fabrikn vu m'hot gemakht meditsinen,

00:20:38.718 --> 00:20:41.318
m'shikt arayn. er hot aleyn oysgearbet, un der

00:20:41.318 --> 00:20:44.938
der yidntum m'hot im lib gehat, er iz gekumen. er hot a mol gekent

00:20:44.938 --> 00:20:46.918
tun a toyve a yid, far vos,

00:20:46.918 --> 00:20:50.960
eyner iz arayngefaln, eyner fun di politsey eynem hot men arestirt eyner vos,

00:20:50.960 --> 00:20:53.998
hot er gekent aroys arbetn m'zol a mentsh bafrayen,

00:20:53.998 --> 00:20:56.856
hot er gehat a shtikl, vi nokh zogt men dos, a shtikl,

00:20:57.553 --> 00:21:00.923
er hot gekent, er iz geven bakant in shtetele.

00:21:00.979 --> 00:21:02.663
hot zi gegebn a shrayb ahine,

00:21:02.663 --> 00:21:06.021
az s'zolt az s'zolt vemen oyfzukhn an Ayznberg,

00:21:06.021 --> 00:21:08.266
un ikh vel zogn ver der tate mayner iz,

00:21:08.266 --> 00:21:13.139
efsher vet dos kenen oysarbetn a PERMIT arayntsukumen in land arayn.

00:21:13.517 --> 00:21:17.341
un s'hot nisht lang gedoyert. m'hot undz geshikt a vize arop,

00:21:17.382 --> 00:21:20.733
undz hobn do dervayl do oysgearbet bay di englisher,

00:21:20.875 --> 00:21:22.826
vayl s'hot nokh gehert ven m'hot,

00:21:23.068 --> 00:21:27.432
s'nokh di englisher zenen do UNK, m'hot badorfn, zey hobn nisht gehat keyn direkte

00:21:27.810 --> 00:21:30.254
opteylung in in Poyln,

00:21:30.254 --> 00:21:35.752
nor s'gegangen nokh der englisher nokh der englisher ambasade tsi vi azoy.

00:21:36.433 --> 00:21:40.758
un m'hot dortn, m'hot undz genumen tsu doktoyrim un m'hot undz ge⟨malet⟩ ir un mir,

00:21:40.758 --> 00:21:45.371
m'hot aroysgegebn a pas, un ale dray peser hot men bashtetikt tsu forn

00:21:45.664 --> 00:21:50.585
keyn Australye. m'hot farshtanen az do iz a vild land, a farvorfn land,

00:21:50.608 --> 00:21:54.399
nor s'beser. Frankraykh iz oykh nisht geven keyn aza laykht lebn nokh der krig,

00:21:54.692 --> 00:21:58.905
azoy az m'hot, m'iz do ahergekumen in zekhtsikstn yor in der ende.

00:21:58.793 --> 00:22:04.625
vos vos far a keyn arbet hostu ir gemakht do?

00:22:03.889 --> 00:22:06.178
do? ikh bin geven in der KNITTING.

00:22:06.893 --> 00:22:09.283
in KNITTING. ikh hob do zeyer a sakh,

00:22:09.441 --> 00:22:14.694
ikh bin geven tsun ersht in a g- a FACTORY nisht azoy groys, s'hot dort gearbet bay a draysik fertsik man,

00:22:14.694 --> 00:22:16.640
tsvey shutfim, yidishe,

00:22:16.714 --> 00:22:22.327
un ikh hob zikh koym oys- s'geven shver tsu krign arbet dem yor vi ikh bin gekumen, s'geven a shtikl krizis do.

00:22:22.553 --> 00:22:28.403
un zey hobn mikh dortn arayngenumen shoyn mit geveyn, mit gebetn vayl zey hobn gehat ful in mentshn,

00:22:28.408 --> 00:22:31.271
un dortn hob ikh opgearbet a gevise tsayt un

00:22:31.834 --> 00:22:34.235
m'tor es nisht redn, zey hobn a bisl mikh

00:22:34.235 --> 00:22:36.884
als yid hobn zey gehat tsu mir a khutspe,

00:22:36.884 --> 00:22:41.154
zey hobn mikh geheysn arbetn OVER TIME, un nisht batsoln,

00:22:41.154 --> 00:22:42.445
un ikh hob im gezogt

00:22:43.225 --> 00:22:47.035
fun akht in der fri biz akhte bay der nakht, s'iz fir sho,

00:22:47.035 --> 00:22:49.935
alts iz aheymgegangen, ikh shtey nokh bay der mashin un arbet.

00:22:50.329 --> 00:22:52.111
hobn zey gezogt,

00:22:52.523 --> 00:22:54.410
"vos vestu aheymgeyn?" zogt er tsu mir,

00:22:54.410 --> 00:22:57.039
eyn balbos. "vest kukn oyfn vayb?

00:22:57.265 --> 00:22:59.807
"du kenst dokh do shteyn bay der mashin aroysgebn skhoyre."

00:23:00.319 --> 00:23:02.979
s'geven azelkhe oysnitsers.

00:23:03.238 --> 00:23:06.674
shoyn un mir iz dortn gevorn shlekht. farshteyst, s'mir gevorn shlekht.

00:23:06.867 --> 00:23:12.362
zey hobn gezogt zey viln mikh opzogn. un ikh hob badorfn oyshaltn di froy, kinderlekh,

00:23:13.127 --> 00:23:16.732
viln mikh opzogn. hob ikh UNK trefn a bakantn,

00:23:17.278 --> 00:23:21.507
er arbet in a groyser un guter FACTORY, Dzhon Krandl.

00:23:21.548 --> 00:23:24.427
geven zeyer bakant in Aus- do in Melburn.

00:23:24.990 --> 00:23:28.156
ikh vel redn mit dem MANAGER fun mayn ⟨Dzhol⟩,

00:23:28.568 --> 00:23:32.645
zogn aza un aza mentsh er hot gearbet in KNITTING far der krig,

00:23:32.770 --> 00:23:35.078
un s'geven primitive mashinen,

00:23:35.078 --> 00:23:40.138
haynt geyen azelkhe mashinen, naye mashinen gebrengt fun Amerike.

00:23:40.583 --> 00:23:44.779
er vet zikh tsugevoynen. er iz in der KNITTING, er vet tsugevoynen zikh.

00:23:44.903 --> 00:23:47.428
un er hot oysgepoyelt bay dem MANAGER

00:23:47.502 --> 00:23:51.191
az ikh zol kumen tsu geyn tsu der arbet. shtel ikh for vos a goy iz,

00:23:51.315 --> 00:23:53.452
un ikh bin geven bay a yid. m'tor nisht redn.

00:23:53.897 --> 00:23:59.252
ikh bin geve- hot mikh der MANAGER avekgezetst zikh bay a mashin, ikh hob nisht gehat di mindste anung

00:23:59.252 --> 00:24:01.943
vos vi azoy art, vi azoy tsu makhn.

00:24:01.943 --> 00:24:06.783
alts iz gegangen oytomatish, aynshteln ruzhne erley modeln,

00:24:06.823 --> 00:24:09.500
di di dem dem di skhoyre aroysgegebn,

00:24:09.523 --> 00:24:12.605
veyst dokh, di fabrikatsye iz geven nisht glat, s'geven

00:24:12.780 --> 00:24:17.414
geven oysgearbet mit mit mit ikh veys, blumen oder azelkhe zakhn.

00:24:18.096 --> 00:24:20.936
m'hot gekent dos makhn. hot er ge- shtel dikh for di firm

00:24:20.936 --> 00:24:23.018
hot mir avekgeshtelt an arbetorer,

00:24:23.040 --> 00:24:25.987
vos er hot shoyn dortn gearbet lang, a krist,

00:24:26.348 --> 00:24:31.657
un er zol shteyn mit mir un er zol mir vayzn yeder shtikl vi azoy m'shtelt di mashin vi azoy.

00:24:31.832 --> 00:24:34.335
un kurts geredt, nokh a vokh tsayt,

00:24:34.335 --> 00:24:39.980
hot er im batsolt di WAGES, un mir gegebn di WAGES far lernen zikh. di FULL WAGES.

00:24:39.980 --> 00:24:44.617
beyde bakrign, ikh hob ongehoybn aleyn tsu arbetn. dort bin ikh avekgezesn sheyne yorn.

00:24:44.927 --> 00:24:46.963
ikh hob arayngenumen dem bruder

00:24:47.020 --> 00:24:50.777
oykhet arayn, er hot nisht gehat keyn shum anung fun keyn KNITTING.

00:24:50.800 --> 00:24:54.829
un er vet zikh oyslernen. ikh hob azoy oykh nisht gezogt dem MANAGER, er vet zikh oyslernen.

00:24:54.829 --> 00:24:56.778
er iz geven far der krig in KNITTING,

00:24:56.778 --> 00:24:59.664
er vet zikh do oykhet khapn, er hot nisht gehat keyn anung fun keyn KNITTING.

00:24:59.664 --> 00:25:02.488
un zey hobn im arayn, der bruder vos iz do hersht nisht lang geshtorbn.

00:25:02.528 --> 00:25:06.060
un zey hobn arayngenumen in FACTORY, er iz dortn gevorn a gantser dos fun a Dzhol,

00:25:06.060 --> 00:25:08.141
er hot zeyer shnel gekhapt dem KNITTING.

00:25:08.569 --> 00:25:13.203
azoy az do hob ikh gearbet a lengere tsayt. m'hot opgearbet bay bay Dzho un Krandl a sheyne yorn,

00:25:13.227 --> 00:25:18.013
un a gevise tsayt hot mayn froy gearbet in a MILK BAR als farkoyfer.

00:25:18.829 --> 00:25:21.945
hot zikh oysgelernt vi azoy m'bahandlt a koyne, vi m-.

00:25:22.390 --> 00:25:26.816
hot zikh di, hot gezogt di balboste, nokh a geviser tsayt zayn dort zogt ir di balboste,

00:25:26.816 --> 00:25:30.452
un un zi hot mikh oysgeredt, zey hobn epes genumen a MILK BAR. in di tsayt

00:25:30.452 --> 00:25:33.410
iz nor geven, der yid hot zikh nor gekhapt tsu a MILK BAR.

00:25:33.493 --> 00:25:36.507
far vos, demolt iz geven di eyntsike parnose vos m'hot gekent fardinen.

00:25:36.767 --> 00:25:42.498
un m'hot yo, m'hot arayn m'hot gefunen a MILK BAR oyf UNK ROAD ergets,

00:25:42.640 --> 00:25:45.598
un m'iz arayn dort, iz geven a yidisher balbos, un

00:25:45.598 --> 00:25:50.413
m'hot zikh oysgedungen, ikh hob im batsolt, ikh hob nokh geborgt fun Hilfs Fund

00:25:50.453 --> 00:25:54.564
a bisl gelt, ikh zol kenen im nokhgebn, vayl ikh hob nisht gehat keyn gelt azoy fil.

00:25:54.942 --> 00:26:00.770
un er hot mikh oykhet, der balbos, oykhet tsu geborgt epes, ikh vel dikh oykhet lozn a bisl, vest mikh bislekhvayz optsoln.

00:26:00.949 --> 00:26:06.495
m'iz arayn in dem MILK BAR, ikh mit der froy, di kinder zenen shoyn gegangen in SCHOOL, zey hobn shoyn gelernt zikh.

00:26:06.923 --> 00:26:11.270
un m'iz dort opgeven in dem MILK BAR, a shver shtikl arbet, tsen yor tsayt.

00:26:12.070 --> 00:26:18.071
un dos iz geven un m'hot gekoyft zikh dos tsu voynen, m'hot zikh gekoyft ayntsushteln in shtub arayn,

00:26:18.195 --> 00:26:23.651
un m'hot fardint gants sheyn. ze'mir geven a tsayt vos der MILK BAR hot gegebn parnose.

00:26:23.651 --> 00:26:27.842
ikh bin geven in Kolfild in yidishn gegnt, ikh hob gehat zeyer a sakh yidishe koynim,

00:26:27.848 --> 00:26:30.258
un raykhe koynim, zey hobn geboyt hayzer,

00:26:30.258 --> 00:26:33.691
un zey hobn nisht gekukt oyf dem oyf der matbeye zey hobn aroysgenumen zikh.

00:26:33.691 --> 00:26:36.920
ikh hob gehat a gevelb bay zikh fun kol-tuv, fun alemen.

00:26:37.129 --> 00:26:39.463
farshteyst, az s'hot gekent araynkumen a greyte

00:26:39.463 --> 00:26:42.838
ovnt broyt makhn far gest. s'ongekumen gest ⟨oystsushteyn⟩

00:26:42.838 --> 00:26:44.753
⟨arayn tsu mir⟩ fil fish fun fun

00:26:44.753 --> 00:26:47.925
geviklte kroyt un ale sortn geven fertik tsu nemen.

00:26:47.925 --> 00:26:52.186
azoy zey hobn zikh gekloybt, a tort, a ruzhne CAKEn gemakhte,

00:26:52.186 --> 00:26:57.173
azoy az zey hobn zikh ayn geven, zey hobn bay undz gemotlt a bisl, arayngekumen farmotlen dos shabes,

00:26:57.173 --> 00:26:59.375
azoy az s'iz geven bay a heymishn arayngeyn.

00:26:59.375 --> 00:27:01.729
un azoy oykh m'hot dortn fardint a por dolar.

00:27:01.729 --> 00:27:03.498
m'hot fun undz alts ayngekoyft.

00:27:03.792 --> 00:27:05.456
un azoy iz geven dos lebn.

00:27:05.293 --> 00:27:05.973
gut.

00:27:05.973 --> 00:27:09.371
un di kinder, vos hobn di kinder gemakhn do?

00:27:07.892 --> 00:27:09.438
di kinder hobn zikh gelernt.

00:27:09.462 --> 00:27:11.150
hobn di gantse tsayt zikh gelernt.

00:27:11.284 --> 00:27:13.235
zey hobn a sakh mol undz

00:27:13.242 --> 00:27:15.677
geheysn far a vokh aroysforn,

00:27:15.677 --> 00:27:17.752
un zey hobn ibergenumen dos gevelb beyde.

00:27:17.752 --> 00:27:20.579
zey hobn zikh fun di shkole, ven s'geven di HOLIDAY,

00:27:20.579 --> 00:27:22.333
aroys fun di SCHOOL,

00:27:22.333 --> 00:27:25.641
un zey hobn zeyer sheyn bahandlt. ven undz zenen nokh tsurikgekumen

00:27:25.641 --> 00:27:28.307
hobn di koynim gezogt s'hot nokh gekent zitsn a por monatn.

00:27:28.307 --> 00:27:34.003
zey hobn undz pre- zenen, neyn, zenen zeyer kinder, voyle kinder, tokhters gor ibergegebene kinder.

00:27:34.003 --> 00:27:38.025
azoy az zey hobn a mol ibergenumen, m'iz avekgeforn oyf HOLIDAYS, in a pensyonar.

00:27:38.436 --> 00:27:41.298
farshteyst, zenen azoy iz gegangen dos gantse lebn.

00:27:41.001 --> 00:27:44.454
ye, un zog mir, vos hobn zey geendikt in der shule?

00:27:43.600 --> 00:27:47.222
der der zun hot geendikt ELECTRONIC inzhenirye,

00:27:47.397 --> 00:27:50.338
un di tokhter hot etlekhe fakultetn, zi

00:27:50.338 --> 00:27:56.435
zi hot geendikt, koydem iz zi geven SCIENCE TEACHER, un hot gelernt in di HIGH SCHOOLS,

00:27:56.458 --> 00:28:02.648
nokh dem hot zi gemakht MASTER OF HIGHER EH OF SCIENCE. MASTER OF SCIENCE.

00:28:02.648 --> 00:28:07.921
nokh dem iz zi arayn, yo in in in dos, in BIOCHEMIST.

00:28:07.921 --> 00:28:11.235
zi hot gearbet in der HOSPITAL a lengere tsayt.

00:28:11.308 --> 00:28:13.529
veyst dokh, genumen di testn fun blut.

00:28:13.924 --> 00:28:18.305
iz di dray ho- hot zi geendikt. dos heyst, yents hot zi nisht geendikt, dem

00:28:18.312 --> 00:28:21.675
SCIENCE OF MASTER OF SCIENCE hot zi gemakht far zikh aleyn

00:28:21.675 --> 00:28:24.518
mer visn. ober nokh dem hot zi nokh gevolt makhn doktorat,

00:28:24.518 --> 00:28:26.270
zi hot nor gevolt shtudirn.

00:28:26.648 --> 00:28:30.944
shoyn un zey hobn beyde zikh gelernt, zey hobn beyde geendikt.

00:28:31.913 --> 00:28:34.981
ken dir fregn, ir kumt fun a

00:28:34.981 --> 00:28:38.234
a frume heym, a khsidishe heym,

00:28:35.794 --> 00:28:37.370
zeyer a frume heym.

00:28:38.443 --> 00:28:44.364
vos far a yidishkeyt gebstu iber in in der heym tsu dayne kinder haynt?

00:28:43.489 --> 00:28:45.120
vos get men yetst?

00:28:44.364 --> 00:28:47.179
neyn, vos du vos ir gebst iber.

00:28:45.328 --> 00:28:46.869
di eyntsike vel ikh zogn,

00:28:46.869 --> 00:28:51.566
di di dos yidishkeyt tsu zey, zey hobn lib di traditsye di yidishe,

00:28:51.623 --> 00:28:56.243
ikh hob geflegt a mol ⟨filn a tam⟩, ober m'vert opgekilt.

00:28:54.660 --> 00:28:56.375
host a mol gefiln?

00:28:56.243 --> 00:29:00.037
neyn a tradi- a traditsyoneln tish nisht azoy.

00:29:00.128 --> 00:29:02.585
fish iz geven, azelkhe zakhn, ober

00:29:02.676 --> 00:29:07.540
di tsore iz geven, di avle iz geven fun mayn zayt vos ikh hob zey nisht gelernt yidish.

00:29:08.228 --> 00:29:12.002
zey zenen arayn in der englisher shprakh arayn azoy vi yunge khevre,

00:29:12.193 --> 00:29:15.574
un ikh hob gekent in der shtub mit zey redn yidish, un dos

00:29:15.574 --> 00:29:18.533
dos biz hay- un zey zenen hobn tsu mir a groyse

00:29:18.707 --> 00:29:22.540
dos, far vos du host undz nisht gelernt keyn yidish. zey hobn gevolt yidish kenen.

00:29:22.808 --> 00:29:26.194
un bay undz in shtub hobn mir geredt sof poylish mit der froy,

00:29:26.284 --> 00:29:29.535
a bisl yidish, di froy iz geven ender in poylish a bisl.

00:29:30.351 --> 00:29:32.184
farshteyst, azoy,

00:29:32.207 --> 00:29:36.217
un ir f- haltst dikh n- noent tsu di kinder?

00:29:35.278 --> 00:29:36.780
BOY!

00:29:36.949 --> 00:29:40.216
ye s'iz der iker, di tokhter iz yetst in Yizrael avekgeforn.

00:29:40.324 --> 00:29:42.781
dortn zi vet kumen, in akhtn darf zi kumen.

00:29:42.805 --> 00:29:44.818
un zi iz shoyn etlekhe mol in Yizrael.

00:29:44.818 --> 00:29:49.549
un undz undz ze'mir shoyn geven tsvey mol in Yizrael, eyn mol far fir monat, eyn mol zeks monat.

00:29:49.639 --> 00:29:52.856
shoyn forndik als turist fun danet.

00:29:52.997 --> 00:29:56.855
tsu di familyen, tsu di froy's familyen, ikh hob gehat dem kuzin dort.

00:29:57.418 --> 00:29:58.964
ikh hob gehat dem bruder dort.

00:29:59.595 --> 00:30:04.131
azoy UNK m'farbrengt biz hayntike tog. ikh bin hersht RETIRED

00:30:04.131 --> 00:30:07.284
shoyn a geshikhte akhtsn yor tsi tsvontsik yor.

00:30:08.117 --> 00:30:09.545
ikh bin shoyn in di yorn.

00:30:11.037 --> 00:30:17.156
un ken dir fregn IF ir bist tsufridn mit dayn lebn do in AUSTRALIA?

00:30:16.200 --> 00:30:17.291
zeyer tsufridn.

00:30:17.314 --> 00:30:19.097
ikh bin ahergekumen fun Poyln

00:30:19.170 --> 00:30:23.369
a khotshik ikh hob nisht gehat keyn gearbet, di ershte hob ikh mikh arum gevalgert, gevezn zeyer shver.

00:30:23.369 --> 00:30:25.444
nor di froy hot gearbet in a HOSPITAL.

00:30:25.444 --> 00:30:28.428
hot zi oykhet geroymt TOILETS, dos iz geven ir arbet.

00:30:28.789 --> 00:30:31.027
un ir gevoynt tsu aza arbet geven?

00:30:31.033 --> 00:30:35.848
un m'hot zi hot mir gegebn a bisl parnose. dos ershte yor hot men gevoynt tsuzamen mit nokh a porfolk,

00:30:35.848 --> 00:30:38.506
oyf a dire, un m'hot beyde getsolt dire gelt,

00:30:38.506 --> 00:30:39.898
un nokh un nakher,

00:30:39.898 --> 00:30:43.340
hob ikh ongehoybn tsu krign arbet bay dem KNITTING, bay di tsvey yidn,

00:30:43.340 --> 00:30:47.328
un s'geven a bisl laykhter, m'hot shoyn gedungen a besere dire, on shutfim,

00:30:47.740 --> 00:30:48.898
AND THAT'S ALL.

00:30:48.988 --> 00:30:50.720
OK. a dank.

00:30:50.580 --> 00:30:51.870
dank dir.

00:30:53.038 --> 00:30:54.014
I THINK WE'RE ON TO
